# Flutter Architecture

- Three layers per feature: presentation, domain, data.
- Widgets render state and dispatch intents only.
- Business rules live in domain use-cases.
- Repository interfaces in domain; implementations in data.
- Shared UI in `lib/shared/widgets/`; core cross-cutting in `lib/core/`.

Load `.cursor/skills/flutter/architecture/SKILL.md` and `.cursor/skills/flutter/riverpod/SKILL.md` when adding features or providers.
